<p>From carpaccio to mini sliders, tagliata to steak and fries, Dim Sum style snacks and more, the choice is amazing, delicious and perfectly presented. Fish, vegetables, salads and sides are all available and beautiful too. Service, as you would expect, is discreet, efficient and impeccable.</p>

